<br>
I am not asking you to post your life story and such, just a simple message would be great.<br>
<br>
Loot - all roads to loots are evil, but that is what the game is about, if you say otherwise then try playing a naked level 60 toon.<br>
<br>
Time and time again, discussion of loot comes into the picture.<br>
<br>
I am of a belief if you are going to guild remove, so be it...<br>
<br>
The guild will not fold because we have lost a few members.<br>
<br>
Take your loot with you, after all its only pixels, but remember those that you have F'd will not forget.<br>
<br>
Those that are deciding about leaving for greener pastures, maybe its best to leave now.<br>
<br>
We may not know everyone in RL, but EQ has become close as it can be.<br>
<br>
Good bye and Good luck to one and all that have/will leave by Guild Remove.<br>
<br>
Tsui<br>
